A curated collection of images representing sign language gestures. This dataset is intended for use in machine learning, computer vision research, educational tools, and accessibility-focused applications.

ğŸ—‚ï¸ Project Overview

This repository contains labeled images of sign language gestures. The primary goal is to support researchers and developers in building models that can recognize sign language signs accurately and help advance accessible communication technologies.

